{"about_the_game":"The Perplexing Orb returns in a brand new entry packed with new features! New art style, new levels, and new game play mechanics!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/Bounce.gif?t=1701456532\" /><br><br>In this third entry to The Perplexing Orb franchise, you have the ability to bounce your way through all new challenges!<br><br>The game contains <strong>40 all new story stages</strong> all designed around distance, height, and the ability to jump!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/CityPixel.gif?t=1701456532\" /><br><br>The game features an all new retro inspired art style with different graphical options. You can either play the game in crisp full HD or with a pixel filter to make the low poly art match closer to the PS1 era aesthetic! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/GraphicOptions1.png?t=1701456532\" /><br><br><strong>INSANE Challenge Mode Levels</strong> make a return in this entry! Once you conquer the main story stages, brace yourself for 8 incredibly difficult stages to test your resolve!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/InsaneChallenges.gif?t=1701456532\" /><br><br>Stage Designs are filled with all sorts of new obstacles and tools like cracking ice, elevators, moving platforms and more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/Elevator1.gif?t=1701456532\" /><br><br><strong>ALL NEW TIME TRIAL MODE.</strong><br>Race for gold medal times OR test yourself against incredibly difficult dev times in the brand new time trial mode!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2679130/extras/T